OL,3,CConvicted murderer has sentence
OL,4,Cextended after attacking officer with
OL,5,Chook shank
OL,7,FA convicted murderer who attacked a
OL,8,Fprison officer with a self-made hook
OL,9,Fshank has had his sentence extended.
OL,11,FChristopher Stubbs, who is serving a
OL,12,Flife sentence at Garth Prison near
OL,13,FLeyland, Lancashire, repeatedly
OL,14,Fstabbed the officer moments after
OL,15,Fmorning unlock.
OL,17,FThe officer he stabbed suffered three
OL,18,Fdeep puncture wounds to his torso and
OL,19,Fabdomen as well as blows to the head.
