OL,7,FIt took several prison officers to
OL,8,Frestrain and subdue Stubbs, while he
OL,9,Fcontinued to hit and bite another
OL,10,Fofficer.
OL,12,FStubbs was sentenced to another 12
OL,13,Fyears in prison at Preston Crown Court
OL,14,Fon 18 December. He is already serving
OL,15,Fa 24 year sentence for a murder he was
OL,16,Fconvicted of in 2016.
