OL,7,FDetective Constable Paul Brown, of
OL,8,FLancashire Police, said: "This was a
OL,9,Fshocking and abhorrent attack on a
OL,10,Fprison officer by a serving inmate
OL,11,Fusing a vicious self-made weapon. "
OL,13,F"It took several prison officers to
OL,14,Frestrain Stubbs, and the judge
OL,15,Fdescribed him as acting liking a rabid
OL,16,Fdog trying to bite them.
OL,18,F"Stubbs is a violent and dangerous
OL,19,Findividual," he added.
