OL,3,CConvicted murderer has sentence
OL,4,Cextended after attacking officer with
OL,5,Chook shank
OL,7,FThe attack happened on 14 July 2024.
OL,8,FLancashire Police said Stubbs was seen
OL,9,Fto "burst out of his cell in an
OL,10,Fagitated state" and go towards the
OL,11,Fother end of the wing, before
OL,12,Fproducing the weapon from his
OL,13,Fwaistband and quickly launching the
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,FThe jury found him guilty of wounding
OL,17,Fwith intent to cause grievous harm,
OL,18,Fassault on an emergency worker, and
OL,19,Fpossession of a sharply pointed
OL,20,Farticle.
